text: Indrė Venskevičiūtė (born 18 December 1991) is a Lithuanian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for A Lyga club MFA Žalgiris Vilnius. She has been a member of the Lithuania women's national team. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
